Keith A. Glascoe https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keith_A._Glascoe 0 Keith Alexander Glascoe (December 9, 1962 – September 11, 2001) was an American actor, firefighter, and a member of the NY Jets practice squad. He was a Firefighter with Ladder 21 of the New York City Fire Department killed in the September 11 attacks.
